cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper discusses methods for updating model filters in visual object tracking, which is a topic within computer vision (cs.CV). The use of discriminative correlation filters (DCF) also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments and visualization techniques used in the paper may also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
